rumor: #Kuwait: An officer with the rank of first lieutenant working in the State Security Service was arrested for obtaining Kuwaiti citizenship by fraud and forgery.
label: SUPPORTS
evidence: Security Media: The General Administration of Relations and Security Media confirms what was circulated on social media about the arrest of an officer in the Ministry of Interior who forged nationality, and the Ministry of Interior will take legal measures against anyone who publishes or publishes false news.
